00:35:55,199 --> 00:35:56,495
Paano ka nangahas, sa harap ni Xiao Chen,

482
00:35:56,519 --> 00:35:58,039
makipaglandian sa ibang lalaki?

483
00:35:59,719 --> 00:36:00,719
Ako...

484
00:36:00,872 --> 00:36:02,392
Ganito ang kinikilos ng girlfriend mo,

485
00:36:03,000 --> 00:36:04,840
at ayaw mo pa ring
makipaghiwalay sa kanya?

486
00:36:08,239 --> 00:36:08,920
Ikaw...

487
00:36:09,039 --> 00:36:11,159
Sinabi mo ba sa boss na girlfriend mo ako?

488
00:36:12,000 --> 00:36:13,615
Huwag mong sabihing may
lihim kang gusto sa akin...

489
00:36:13,639 --> 00:36:14,679
at hindi ko man lang nalaman?

490
00:36:14,840 --> 00:36:17,360
Cheng Yichen, kasuklam-suklam kang hatak.

491
00:36:22,679 --> 00:36:23,679
Pasensya na.

492
00:36:24,280 --> 00:36:25,400
Mukhang na-misunderstood ako.

493
00:36:25,880 --> 00:36:26,880
Weyter.

494
00:36:27,039 --> 00:36:28,039
Ang menu.

495
00:36:34,719 --> 00:36:35,880
Sige, pupunta na kami kung ganoon.

496
00:36:36,719 --> 00:36:37,719
Hayaan mong isakay kita.

497
00:36:39,039 --> 00:36:39,880
Dating kaklase.

498
00:36:40,000 --> 00:36:41,000
Hindi, salamat.

499
00:36:41,800 --> 00:36:42,800
Papunta na ako.

500
00:36:44,079 --> 00:36:45,079
Sumama ka sa akin.

501
00:36:46,440 --> 00:36:47,839
A-aalis na kami, Yichen.

502
00:36:47,840 --> 00:36:48,880
Salamat sa hapunan, Ginoong Lu.

503
00:36:49,079 --> 00:36:50,360
Paalam. Tara na, tara na.

504
00:36:58,480 --> 00:36:59,480
Uminom.

505
00:36:59,960 --> 00:37:01,639
Hindi mo naman talaga gusto si Yichen, 'di ba?

506
00:37:41,519 --> 00:37:42,519
Nauuhaw ako.

507
00:37:42,800 --> 00:37:44,560
Tara, punta tayo sa bahay mo
para uminom ng tubig.

508
00:37:51,480 --> 00:37:52,039
Ano?

509
00:37:52,119 --> 00:37:53,159
Sandali lang.

510
00:38:00,559 --> 00:38:02,000
Xiao Chen, anong ginagawa mo?

511
00:38:02,840 --> 00:38:03,960
May tao ba diyan sa loob?

512
00:38:05,480 --> 00:38:06,480
Buksan ang pinto.

513
00:38:07,159 --> 00:38:08,159
Cheng Yichen.

514
00:38:23,599 --> 00:38:24,880
Kasama mo ang lugar na ito, 'di ba?

515
00:38:26,280 --> 00:38:27,440
Mukhang maganda.

516
00:38:27,773 --> 00:38:28,773
Medyo maliit lang.

517
00:38:30,440 --> 00:38:32,040
Bakit hindi ka na lang tumira sa mas magandang apartment?

518
00:38:32,119 --> 00:38:34,400
Grabe ang taas ng upa dito sa paligid.

519
00:38:34,960 --> 00:38:36,919
Sa unang taon ko pagkatapos
ng graduation, dito ako nakatira...

520
00:38:36,920 --> 00:38:38,639
ay medyo maayos na.

521
00:38:39,519 --> 00:38:41,400
Hindi madalas umuuwi ang roommate ko,

522
00:38:41,519 --> 00:38:44,159
kaya ako lang talaga ang may lugar na ito.

523
00:38:48,119 --> 00:38:49,360
Ano ang gusto mong inumin?

524
00:38:49,519 --> 00:38:50,519
Walang pulang alak.

525
00:38:53,647 --> 00:38:54,727
Gusto ko...

526
00:38:56,280 --> 00:38:57,280
katas ng dalandan.

527
00:38:59,760 --> 00:39:00,960
Magpanggap na parang nasa bahay ka lang.

528
00:39:41,639 --> 00:39:42,639
Paano naman...

529
00:39:43,199 --> 00:39:44,440
manonood tayo ng sine?

530
00:39:45,559 --> 00:39:47,359
- Ikaw...
- Matagal na akong hindi nanood ng sine.

531
00:39:48,119 --> 00:39:50,400
Hindi ka ba... busy?

532
00:39:52,239 --> 00:39:54,360
Plano ko
pa naman sanang magpahinga ngayon.

533
00:40:45,480 --> 00:40:46,880
Hindi naman talaga sentimental.

534
00:40:47,679 --> 00:40:49,079
Tunay na gawa ng isang maestro.

535
00:40:49,880 --> 00:40:51,400
Habang lalong naghihirap ang mga manonood,

536
00:40:52,420 --> 00:40:53,880
habang lumalamig ang kamera.

537
00:40:58,519 --> 00:40:59,880
Tunay na paghihirap...

538
00:41:01,599 --> 00:41:03,639
ay isang bagay na
hindi mo man lang maipahayag sa mga salita.
